description: Most of the back wall of the lobby is comprised of a detailed raised mural done in bold colors.  Soft chimes emit from the crystal prisms of the chandelier hanging overhead as it slowly rotates on its chain.  High-backed chairs encircle a silver serving cart containing both hot and cold drinks and a few snacks.  Strange symbols border the edges of arched openings located at both ends of the hall.  At the back of the rectangular chamber, an ivory inlaid door stands ajar.
title: [Rhyaesdid Hall, Lower Level]
